comments: During the pick, Gallinari (ATL) and Strus (MIA) briefly engage and disengage and the contact is marginal.
Gallinari (ATL) legally contests Herro's (MIA) jump shot attempt.  He steps forward but does not step into Herro's landing area.
Strus (MIA) places a hand on Young's (ATL) body and the contact is marginal during his driving shot attempt.
Strus (MIA) briefly places a hand/arm to the front of Young (ATL) but the contact is marginal and does not affect his SQBR.
Huerter (ATL) commits a take foul on Herro (MIA).
Butler (MIA) legally contests Bogdanovic's (ATL) jump shot attempt.
